{"tid":1923841,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"領養Sulli生前愛貓　金善兒發文多謝希澈","createTime":"2020-03-13T09:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T18:22:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1dc96f1782624c9e14a298a9ec5d472a91da683f","tid":1923841,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:59:03.000Z","msg":"生前飽受網上惡評困擾的韓國女團f(x)前成員Sulli，去年10月14日在家中上吊自殺離世，終年25歲，震驚演藝界，曾經十分照顧Sulli的同門師兄Super Junior成員希澈，代為照顧Sulli生前的愛貓Goblin，而Sulli的好友金善兒今日上載多謝Goblin的照片，又公開她錫錫Goblin的短片，透露最近已經將Goblin接到家中。<br />\n<br />\n金善兒坦言在Sulli離世後，沒有信心可以立即照顧Goblin，亦因為看到Goblin時，就會因為想起Sulli而感到很難過，於是小心地拜託希澈代為照顧：「他完全沒有考慮，馬上就答應幫我照顧牠，帶牠去做健康檢查，真的非常感謝他，我好感動，他真的是很帥氣的人。」<br />\n<br />\n她又指自己在做好心理準備後，已經正式領養Goblin：「雖然已經過了一段時間，但這麼可愛的孩子，只有我自己一個人看到實在太可惜了，所以小心翼翼地跟大家分享，Goblin你是最好的，我愛你。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200313/bkn-20200313170402324-0313_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200313%2Fbkn-20200313170402324-0313_00862_001.html&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=d260daf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200313/bkn-20200313170402324-0313_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e0305333ad461261f7b61b5ee6c632b81ff8e550","tid":1923841,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"希澈完美男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cc7180d361f0f48a8aff922df4268d0c3c4325","tid":1923841,"uid":74435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T17:52:30.000Z","msg":"親哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eaaacc71c0cd6dc4aad20332c0bf36b4837d405","tid":1923841,"uid":323551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:22:05.000Z","msg":"搞隻貓好啦，唔好搞MoMo"}]}